225.title: Prohibited Discrimination
225.description: Provides that sexual orientation & gender identity are impermissible grounds for discrimination in public lodging establishments & public food service establishments; revises provisions of Florida Civil Rights Act of 1992 & Fair Housing Act to include sexual orientation & gender identity; provides exception for constitutionally protected free exercise of religion.

351.title: Crimes Evidencing Prejudice
351.description: Requires grounds for reclassification of crimes to include prejudice based on gender or gender identity of any person; defines "gender identity"; requires grounds for reclassification of crimes to include prejudice based on disability of any person; revises definition of term "disability."
